<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Outfit", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #18181b;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 24px;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(24,24,27,0.08), 0 0 0 1px rgba(24,24,27,0.06);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background: #0d9488;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 24px 28px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 24px 28px;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #18181b;
    }
    .body p {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .body p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #0d9488;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 10px 24px;
      border-radius: 26px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 16px 28px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(24,24,27,0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #71717a;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0d9488;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer p {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
    }
    .footer p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>{{content}}</p>
      <a href="{{baseUrl}}" class="btn">Megtekintés a Filcben</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Ez az email a Filc rendszer automatikus üzenete.</p>
      <p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Leiratkozás az értesítésekről</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
